Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,==========正文==========
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.99,0:01:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開玲子的遺物幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.02,0:01:44.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.56,0:01:47.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  倒不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.33,0:01:49.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.00,0:01:53.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺  一如既往地讓人搞不懂的傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.61,0:01:56.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粘上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.35,0:02:00.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西瓜籽  嘴兩邊  兩粒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.92,0:02:02.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意  不知不覺而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.47,0:02:04.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白你的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.51,0:02:07.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次還給妖怪名字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.72,0:02:13.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲子的記憶成為思念  注入我的內心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.72,0:02:17.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲子這個人  一點點地…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.60,0:02:30.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向圖書館借的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.61,0:02:32.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是忘記還了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.87,0:02:36.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車票？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.47,0:02:46.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.62,0:02:49.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.43,0:02:52.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得是哪方錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.09,0:02:57.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙說油炸豆腐清湯麵里的豆腐是先吃的  難以置信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.06,0:02:59.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是先吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.19,0:03:01.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.56,0:03:05.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豆腐是要浸在湯汁裏最後吃的  是吧夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.40,0:03:09.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  豆腐是要趁甜味沒有被湯汁沖淡前吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.11,0:03:11.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的吧  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.73,0:03:15.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…我是覺得怎麼都可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.39,0:03:16.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.39,0:03:17.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豆腐要後吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.81,0:03:19.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豆腐要先吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.98,0:03:23.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這麼爭論之前  那個不叫豆腐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.41,0:03:28.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個怎麼都行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.84,0:03:29.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:30.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是後吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.20,0:03:31.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先吃對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:32.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.21,0:03:33.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕交
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.92,0:03:35.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  正和我意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.14,0:03:40.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無聊的爭吵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.05,0:03:43.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  你掉的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.73,0:03:48.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是過去的車票吧  怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.83,0:03:50.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.83,0:03:53.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟夏目有什麼關係呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.84,0:03:56.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有什麼說道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:04:00.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣…今早上學時撿到的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.20,0:04:02.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拙劣的謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.19,0:04:08.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.47,0:04:10.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等會再好好問你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.30,0:04:17.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.84,0:04:20.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃也沒用哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.27,0:04:21.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.25,0:04:23.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪裏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:25.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏…回家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.72,0:04:28.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要去那張車票的站頭吧  一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.82,0:04:31.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車站在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:33.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才沒看清楚  忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.28,0:04:34.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在附近嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:37.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fscx80\fscy92\fnDFPTFLeiSho-W5}屜{\r}田  你為什麼這麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.02,0:04:39.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:45.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  自上次的試膽大會以來  我真的想見個面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.10,0:04:46.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見誰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.91,0:04:49.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見誰  你真討厭  這不明擺著的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.85,0:04:51.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧  車來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.33,0:04:53.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們上車吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.79,0:04:55.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你掉東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.99,0:04:58.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.18,0:05:02.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.75,0:05:07.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒掉東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.59,0:05:08.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.93,0:05:09.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.19,0:05:10.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.37,0:05:11.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.17,0:05:14.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:17.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.81,0:05:21.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.99,0:05:25.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊  到底我掉了什麼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.41,0:05:28.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.29,0:05:50.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算來了嗎  真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.94,0:05:51.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓咪老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.23,0:05:58.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏已經不使用了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.80,0:06:03.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好像很久之前就成為廢線了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.72,0:06:05.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真凄涼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:09.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霧沼是在另一邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:12.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過為什麼玲子又…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:22.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.49,0:06:24.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼熱還真虧它能睡著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.17,0:06:31.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.51,0:06:36.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是玲子  終於來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:38.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:40.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  別搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.14,0:06:42.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是玲子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.93,0:06:44.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.37,0:06:49.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是玲子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.81,0:06:53.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  我不是玲子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.52,0:06:56.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  想點辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.96,0:06:59.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在說什麼都沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:02.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是什麼壞東西  你就陪他玩一會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.11,0:07:04.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什  什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.00,0:07:06.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.61,0:07:08.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.89,0:07:15.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  玲子死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.61,0:07:18.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能明白真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.77,0:07:22.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是孫子嘛  氣味相似也不足為奇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.70,0:07:26.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用聞得這麼細緻入微
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.28,0:07:28.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  濃毛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.58,0:07:33.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說在這裏等玲子  是不是有什麼約定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.60,0:07:36.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  她說會和我一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.59,0:07:38.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:39.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.50,0:07:48.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霧沼  玲子要和你一起去霧沼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.83,0:07:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  霧沼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.59,0:07:52.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.88,0:07:54.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:59.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗡嗡地叫  說「不會原諒你的」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:02.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是玲子就說「不行啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:04.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.62,0:08:08.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓這傢伙來說明還真是為難呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.20,0:08:11.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許這傢伙在友人帳上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.94,0:08:15.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把名字還給它的話  思念會傳達給我們事由的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.04,0:08:16.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.21,0:08:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你名字是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.91,0:08:21.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字  我叫三都
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.67,0:08:22.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三都
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.38,0:08:25.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾之守護喲  昭顯其名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.09,0:08:44.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵架了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.59,0:08:48.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生氣的是實栗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.64,0:08:52.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡那個叫實栗的妖怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.33,0:08:56.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡實栗了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.51,0:09:02.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是實栗說討厭我  不想再見我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.19,0:09:05.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做錯什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.60,0:09:09.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不記得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.70,0:09:15.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那實栗對你說了什麼生氣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.13,0:09:23.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像多少有點明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.36,0:09:24.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實栗生氣的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.48,0:09:27.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦啊  玲子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.04,0:09:29.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實栗現在在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.01,0:09:31.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霧沼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.73,0:09:33.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霧沼  鄰站的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.79,0:09:39.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了  那我和你一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.48,0:09:42.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.46,0:09:49.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過今天天色已晚  明天再在此碰頭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.11,0:09:52.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲子  謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很癢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:09:57.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  三都
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.69,0:10:06.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  沒能完成約定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.45,0:10:11.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是玲子有了什麼不能來的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.69,0:10:14.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.39,0:10:19.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方可能已經不在等待了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.39,0:10:22.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去一下是不會知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.27,0:10:27.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去  要完成玲子沒做完的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.43,0:10:32.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過今天天色已晚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.27,0:10:35.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天放學後我過來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.59,0:10:46.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了  還是現在就動身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.88,0:10:51.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  輕易就答應
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.98,0:10:54.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霧沼附近可沒有公交車通過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:58.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道走過去要多久嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:01.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那肯定天都黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.98,0:11:10.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是白說了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.91,0:11:27.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  三都
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.59,0:11:31.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲子不來的話  你一個人不也可以去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.63,0:11:34.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼就這麼傻等著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.53,0:11:39.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為約好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.44,0:11:41.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真傻  居然去問他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.11,0:11:51.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始變冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.36,0:11:54.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像山間的寒風在流入
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.49,0:11:56.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  三都
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.50,0:12:10.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說這傢伙是可愛呢還是煩人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.70,0:12:17.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三都
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.78,0:12:21.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見到實栗的話  準備怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.91,0:12:24.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼  沒想過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.93,0:12:29.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和好的話  得說點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.79,0:12:32.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.85,0:12:38.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是別讓他們見面比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:41.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許反而會變麻煩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.97,0:12:44.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.00,0:12:47.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三都  在到達之前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.41,0:12:48.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想好要說些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:51.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.11,0:12:52.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.99,0:12:53.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.89,0:12:56.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.30,0:12:57.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.50,0:12:59.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怨念
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨念？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.47,0:13:10.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三都
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.02,0:13:15.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會原諒  不會原諒你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.25,0:13:18.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.16,0:13:30.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.19,0:13:31.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓穩咯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.35,0:13:35.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.36,0:13:37.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標是三都
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.86,0:13:38.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:41.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來實栗被地靈附身了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.99,0:13:42.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被地靈…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.38,0:13:45.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為地靈喜好憤怒及仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:49.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實栗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.44,0:13:51.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實栗對三都如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.42,0:13:54.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不要去見對方為好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.37,0:14:00.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼做  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:02.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實栗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:04.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.15,0:14:06.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得怎樣我都不管了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:10.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去啊  貓咪老師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.92,0:14:12.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.65,0:14:33.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷啊  彷彿不是夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.06,0:14:35.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是山間的寒風
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:36.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怨念所致吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.38,0:14:40.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實栗  出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.03,0:14:45.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實栗  有話要跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.68,0:14:53.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三都  實栗長什麼樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.17,0:14:56.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…小小的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.24,0:14:59.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小的  是多小
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.01,0:15:09.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼小嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.03,0:15:19.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個大小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.25,0:15:30.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是開玩笑的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.90,0:15:32.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼在  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.50,0:15:36.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.49,0:15:45.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現形吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.34,0:15:59.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…魚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.03,0:16:01.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實栗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.14,0:16:02.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那就是實栗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.22,0:16:05.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分明是奇大無比啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.99,0:16:09.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦夏目  要說服它嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.21,0:16:18.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為我是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.54,0:16:24.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:35.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子  是夏目玲子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.50,0:16:40.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來得正好  把友人帳交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.57,0:16:45.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友人帳在那裏面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:52.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.14,0:16:54.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是玲子的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.29,0:16:56.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我  蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.18,0:17:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實栗  實栗  是我  三都
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.39,0:17:05.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我不好  快醒過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.16,0:17:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實栗  快回來  求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.40,0:17:10.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三都
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.65,0:17:12.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把友人帳給我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.33,0:17:15.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  不給
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.62,0:17:16.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.27,0:17:44.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.12,0:17:47.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.94,0:17:50.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.20,0:17:51.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.43,0:17:54.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實栗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:18:00.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很可憐  看來跟地靈一起消失在沼澤底了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.49,0:18:03.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三都
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.69,0:18:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  到底搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.35,0:18:16.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  三都你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.84,0:18:18.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實栗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.84,0:18:21.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  要幹什麼笨蛋  放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.36,0:18:22.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.96,0:18:24.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實栗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.57,0:18:27.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣  很噁心啊  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.69,0:18:29.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說放開我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.78,0:18:36.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  吵架是因為玲子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.33,0:18:38.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  因為夏目玲子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.01,0:18:41.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.39,0:18:43.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.70,0:18:46.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這蠢貨把重要的名字給了玲子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.22,0:18:48.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:52.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有作為妖怪的自尊嗎  你這大蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.87,0:18:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來再也不想見你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.61,0:18:58.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻又恬不知恥地出現了  你這呆瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.31,0:18:59.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.80,0:19:03.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  不用這麼說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.90,0:19:07.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三都喜歡你  所以一直牽掛著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.67,0:19:08.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說它蠢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.24,0:19:11.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有心道歉的話給我快點過來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.33,0:19:12.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直心不在焉的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.49,0:19:14.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.08,0:19:14.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.48,0:19:16.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.30,0:19:16.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  實栗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.65,0:19:18.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  看仔細了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.20,0:19:21.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  有在聽嗎濃毛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.07,0:19:23.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在跟你說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.26,0:19:25.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.70,0:19:29.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩個傢伙  早就和好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.13,0:19:33.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實栗  我們回山裏去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:34.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你說也會回去的  你個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.48,0:19:39.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  真的謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.08,0:19:41.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  別向人類低頭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.23,0:19:44.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  他把名字也還給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.32,0:19:46.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.72,0:19:50.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說別低頭了  你這笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.21,0:20:02.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼  又不知不覺了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.86,0:20:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是把它放回原處啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.42,0:20:10.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說玲子沒能完成約定是因為有特別的原因對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:13.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太瞧得起她了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.32,0:20:16.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一不小心忘記了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.58,0:20:18.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲子就是這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.19,0:20:20.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼隨便…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.03,0:20:22.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這書是怎麼回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.99,0:20:26.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是藉著沒還嗎  瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.64,0:20:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.29,0:20:35.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  看來忘了不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.45,0:20:39.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去真像是有特別原因呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.68,0:20:42.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  玲子啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.61,0:20:48.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.92,0:20:50.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早…早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.45,0:20:52.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.24,0:20:55.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們和好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.66,0:21:01.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天那算是什麼啊  真莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.86,0:21:04.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因為是好朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.41,0:21:12.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  昨天怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.78,0:21:17.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了  想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:19.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失陪一下  這個拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.64,0:21:21.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.56,0:21:22.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fscx80\fscy92\fnDFPTFLeiSho-W5}屜{\r}田  {\fe128\fscx80\fscy92\fnDFPTFLeiSho-W5}屜{\r}田
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.43,0:21:27.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天婦羅麵條裏的蝦  你是先吃還是後吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.31,0:21:29.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西怎樣都好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.41,0:21:37.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好朋友…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.95,0:21:43.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天  謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.37,0:21:46.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到你很為難嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.83,0:23:38.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉入了水壩的村子出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.05,0:23:42.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棲身在那的妖怪們為了要回名字而來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.24,0:23:44.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你這傢伙  別纏住夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.73,0:23:46.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想見一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.54,0:23:48.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時要麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.91,0:23:50.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想見的人…
